    <note type="biography">
        <p>Botanist. Brought up a printer. Emigrated to the United States in 1807. Travelled in America from about 1811 to 1834; made a number of botanical discoveries. Curator of the botanic gardens and professor of natural history, Harvard University, 1825–34. Returned to England in 1842. Author of many works on North American plants.</p></note>
    <note type="sources">
        <p>R. Desmond 1977, <hi rend="italic">Modern English biography</hi>.</p>
